version_description:
Introducing a brand new 3.0 version of Reps Calculator!
- Completely revamped UI
- New theme colors for pro users
- (Finally) Optimized for larger iPhone screens
- Ability to Share your lifts with your friends

And as always if you like Reps Calculator, please rate it on the app store or send feedback with your thoughts!

Welcome to the newest version of 1RM Calculator!

Built from the ground up, 1RM Calculator has been redesigned and reimagined to make this the easiest and simplest method to calculate your one rep max.
